<style>
.features { padding:80px 0;background:var(--brand-light); }
.ft-title { text-align:center;font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:48px;letter-spacing:-.5px;color:var(--brand-dark); }
.ft-grid { display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px; }
.ft-card { background:var(--brand-white);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:36px 28px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06);transition:box-shadow .3s; }
.ft-card:hover { box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(31,105,240,.12); }
.ft-icon { font-size:36px;margin-bottom:16px; }
.ft-card h3 { font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--brand-dark); }
.ft-card p { font-size:14px;color:var(--brand-gray);line-height:1.5; }
@media (max-width:768px) { .ft-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
</style>

<section class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="ft-title">Why VertiKnee™</h2>
    <div class="ft-grid">
      <div class="ft-card"><div class="ft-icon">🧬</div><h3>3D Anatomic Compression</h3><p>Targets the patellar tendon with precision — reduces the exact impact that causes downhill knee pain.</p></div>
      <div class="ft-card"><div class="ft-icon">🫁</div><h3>Breathable Tech Fabric</h3><p>Moisture-wicking 4-way stretch. Stays dry and comfortable after 8+ hours on the trail.</p></div>
      <div class="ft-card"><div class="ft-icon">🛡️</div><h3>Anti-Slip Silicone Grip</h3><p>Inner gel strips lock the sleeve in place. Never rolls down mid-hike.</p></div>
      <div class="ft-card"><div class="ft-icon">⚡</div><h3>Ultralight 80g</h3><p>You'll forget you're wearing it — until you realize you've done 15km pain-free.</p></div>
      <div class="ft-card"><div class="ft-icon">🎒</div><h3>Packs Flat</h3><p>Roll it, fold it, clip it to your pack. Zero bulk. Always trail-ready.</p></div>
      <div class="ft-card"><div class="ft-icon">🔄</div><h3>30-Day Trail Guarantee</h3><p>Take it on 3 hikes. If your knees don't feel better, full refund. No questions.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% schema %}{"name":"Features","settings":[],"presets":[{"name":"Features"}]}{% endschema %}
